  "prompt": "What are the best online shopping aggregators? For deals, comparisons, etc.",
  "response": "There are several excellent online shopping aggregators that help you find the best deals, compare prices, and discover promotions. Here are some of the best ones:\n\n1. **Google Shopping**: This service allows you to search for items across multiple online retailers, compare prices, and read product reviews.\n\n2. **PriceGrabber**: Known for its extensive price comparison capabilities, PriceGrabber lets you find the best deals on a wide range of products from numerous online stores.\n\n3. **ShopSavvy**: Available as both a website and a mobile app, ShopSavvy provides price comparisons, product reviews, and can notify you of price drops on items you\u2019re interested in.\n\n4. **CamelCamelCamel**: This is a popular price tracker for Amazon products. It helps you monitor price changes, set alerts, and check historical pricing data to make informed purchasing decisions.\n\n5. **Honey**: Honey is a browser extension that automatically finds and applies coupon codes at checkout, and also offers tools for price tracking and comparing similar items.\n\n6. **RetailMeNot**: While primarily focused on coupons and promo codes, RetailMeNot also offers cash back deals and aggregates discounts from a variety of retailers.\n\n7. **Shopzilla**: This comparison shopping site covers a wide range of products and provides reviews, ratings, and pricing information from different retailers.\n\n8. **BizRate**: BizRate gives users access to product comparisons, price tracking, and extensive reviews to help make purchasing decisions easier.\n\n9. **PriceSpy**: A comprehensive price comparison tool, PriceSpy covers electronics, fashion, sports equipment, and more, with price history charts and detailed product information.\n\n10. **Slickdeals**: This community-driven site features user-posted deals, coupons, and discounts across various categories, ensuring you get the best possible price.\n\nThese aggregators can help you efficiently navigate through numerous online retailers and make informed purchasing decisions to save money and get the best deals.",
